show.name: Soul Land
show.summary: Тан Сан провел свою жизнь во Внешней секте Тан, посвятив себя созданию и освоению скрытого оружия. Как только он украл тайные знания Внутренней Секты, чтобы достичь вершины своего искусства, его единственным выходом была смерть. Но после того, как он сбросился со смертоносного Пика Ада, он переродился в другом мире, мире Доуло Далу, мире, где у каждого человека есть собственный дух, и те, у кого сильный дух, могут практиковать свою духовную силу, чтобы подняться и стать Духом. Мастера. @@Дух, который пробуждается в Тан Сане, — это Голубая Серебряная Трава, бесполезный дух. Сможет ли он преодолеть трудности, чтобы достичь высоких званий духовных мастеров и принести славу секты Тан в этот новый мир?

show.name: To Get Her
show.summary:
Having known each other since they were young, Tu Si Yi and Lin Zheng Zheng were originally a happy couple. When Tu Si Yi debuted as an idol, fame got in the way of their relationship and they drove them apart. Tu Si Yi starts endorsing a game and suddenly gets trapped inside it to become the 3rd prince and protagonist of the story. To save her boyfriend, Lin Zheng Zheng enters the game as a player and realizes that she is the 3rd princess and the villain. With only the three lives allotted in the game, Lin Zheng Zheng must assist Tu Si Yi in becoming king. However, Tu Si Yi has lost all of his memories and considers Zheng Zheng to be his biggest enemy. His subconscious also has no interest in the throne as he enjoys the music instead. Will the two ever find their way out of the game and into each other's arms again? 

(Source: chinesedrama.info)

show.name: SciShow
show.summary:
SciShow explores the unexpected. Seven days a week, Hank Green, Michael Aranda, and Olivia Gordon delve into the scientific subjects that defy our expectations and make us even more curious!

Schedule:

Sundays — Learn about the amazing topics we can't quite make a stand-alone show about in SciShow List Show!

Mondays — Tune in for a short Dose about our weird world.

Tuesdays — Find answers to our most asked Quick Questions.

Wednesdays — Hank or Michael dives deep into a long-form Infusion episode, or an unscripted talk show or quiz show with a guest!

Thursday — Another new dose about the wonders of the world.

Fridays — Learn the latest in science News.

Saturdays — Get your quick questions answered!

show.name: Until We Meet Again
show.summary:
Thirty years ago, Korn and Intouch were university students in Bangkok. Intouch entered into Korn's life despite knowing that he was a son of the most influential people. At first, Korn kept pushing Intouch away, but in the end, he could not resist Intouch who was so full of life and decided to let him into his heart. However, homosexuality was unacceptable at the time, and so their parents were against their relationship. While Intouch kept fighting for their future, Korn could not deal with all the sufferings and decided to give up. Their story ended with tragedy, but something has tied them together even after they were dead. 

Years after, Pharm (Intouch's reincarnation), always feels that he is waiting to meet 'someone.' Dean (Korn's reincarnation) also spends his entire life searching for 'the one.' The red thread of fate will bring them together and ties them to the past that is not worth remembering.
